% if_fails_do(Goal, ExceptionHandler)
if_fails_do(Goal, _ExceptionHandler):- call(Goal), !.
if_fails_do(_Goal, ExceptionHandler):- call(ExceptionHandler), fail.

implies(Ant, Cons):- call(Ant), !, call(Cons).
implies(_Ant, _Cons).

