next(N,Nn):- not(var(N)),  !, Nn is  N + 1.
next(N,Nn):- not(var(Nn)), !, N  is Nn - 1.

next_90_clockwise(n, e).
next_90_clockwise(e, s).
next_90_clockwise(s, w).
